rule was deemed necessary because of (1) comments received on the original proposed rule published on June 19, 1992,
and (2) regulations issued by the Agricultural Marketing Service concerning the pricing of milk used to produce nonfat
dry milk after the publication of the original proposed rule for section 102. The supplemental proposed rule specified
that all comments had to be received by January 31, 1994, in order to be assured of consideration. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
