proposal is to reclassify a portion of the current Class D airspace extension at Roswell, NM to a Class E airspace extension
to contain instrument approach procedures and to provide adequate Class D airspace to contain IFR operations and
require two-way radio communications at Roswell Industrial Air Center.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
