<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
Designate a lead agency for motorcycle safety;
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Develop funding sources;
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Collect and analyze data on motorcycle safety;
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Identify the State's motorcycle safety problem areas;
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Develop programs (with specific projects) to address problems;
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Coordinate motorcycle projects with those for the general motoring public; and
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Integrate motorcycle safety into community traffic safety programs.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
II. Motorcycle Personal Protective Equipment
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

