Motorcycle helmets (which should be required by law);
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Proper clothing, including gloves, boots, long pants, and a durable long-sleeved jacket; and
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Eye (which should be required by law) and face protection.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 04 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

