programs and other advocacy groups in evaluating whether the goals stated in the plan adequately reflect the anticipated
potential for subcontracting to small, small disadvantaged, and women-owned small business concerns; and
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(4) Review, when applicable, the offeror's description of its strategies, historical performance and significant
achievements in placing subcontracts for the same or similar products or services with small, small disadvantaged,
and women-owned small business concerns.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(d) Failure to submit to subcontracting plan and/or correct deficiencies in the plan within the time specified by
the Contracting Officer shall make the offeror ineligible for award.
